author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Join me for this exclusive interview with the Residence of Evil crew, who are putting together a crowdfunded fan movie - Resident Evil: Resurrection, feating the original live action cast from the 1996 classic. And they're all here to chat and answer questions! 

Subscribe to the Residence of Evil channel: https://www.youtube.com/@ROEnetwork
title: Resident Evil: Resurrection (feat. The Entire Resident Evil Cast)
